{"tid":944626,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查時間最長　聲明歷來最短","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T09:36:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"de4628b6b745ef40092988eb0c39d76d1c019200","tid":944626,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181217/20570456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570456&d=38KyZA03mmW%2Bd8urcvfUcZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=1ab9af35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181217%2F20570456&h=82c2f7ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181217/20570456</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月17日 <br />\n<br />\n調查時間最長　聲明歷來最短<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181217/large/1213wing0455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181217%2Flarge%2F1213wing0455.jpg&h=44d968ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前特首梁振英涉及的UGL案，律政司司長鄭若驊最終以證據不足為由決定不提檢控，但當日律政司未有召開記者會，只以簡單一頁紙聲明宣佈作罷，至今未公開詳細交代，諷刺的是相對回歸後涉及不少公職人員的案件調查，UGL案調查時間卻是最長，由2014年中被揭發到近日有調查結果，歷時長達四年，但律政司的聲明卻是歷來最短的一次，難怪未能釋除坊間疑慮，民主派指鄭若驊必須親身交代以釋疑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者許偉賢、林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：百人遊行抗議UGL案放生689泛民六問龜縮鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181217/large/a0202a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181217%2Flarge%2Fa0202a.gif&h=7df3c006&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n百人遊行抗議UGL案放生689　泛民六問龜縮鄭若驊<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：梁振英疑聽命收聲 (季陶)"}]}